data.description: This home is available- make it yours! 2 Car Parking!! Impeccably maintained Roxborough/Manayunk townhome in the coveted "Valley View" community. No HOA. This 4-story luxury gem boasts a 1-car attached garage and an additional parking spot. With 2475 sq ft, the ground floor welcomes you with a spacious entry area, updated Powder Room, storage closet, and access to an over-sized garage. The main floor features a modern open floor plan, including a fully equipped Kitchen with granite countertops, a large sit-down island, and stainless-steel appliances. The Formal Dining area leads to a rear balcony, while the living room is complemented by cherry-stained Oak H/W flooring, 9' ceilings, and recessed lighting.   On the second level, discover a convenient hall laundry area and two generously sized bedrooms, each with double closets and full baths. The entire upper level is dedicated to a vast Main Bedroom with three closets and a sitting area, tastefully updated for versatile use - be it a bonus room, theater, or office. Throughout, enjoy the care and attention given to the property, with pristine paint and carpet.   This residence offers the convenience of walking to Main Street Manayunk, Ridge Ave, and Septa, with easy access to Center City, the Mainline, KOP, and major roads. Move right in and relish a lifestyle of comfort and style. Showings are a breeze—don't miss out on this delightful home!
